com.logtracking.lib.api.config

Class EmailLogSendingConfiguration

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.logtracking.lib.api.config.EmailLogSendingConfiguration
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    LogSendingConfiguration

    public final class EmailLogSendingConfiguration
extends java.lang.Object
implements LogSendingConfiguration
    Class represents config of sending issue report by e-mail. Default supported e-mail server is GMAIL, for supporting other servers for sending , you should set correct "e-mail host" parameter for server you use.
